计算2的n次幂代码，粘贴即可
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>计算2的n次幂</title>
    <style>
        h4 {
           color:brown
         }
         
    </style>
      <script>
          var n = parseInt(window.prompt('计算2的n次幂，只需输入数字即可'));
           var qiuruikai = 1;
           for (var i = 0;i < n;i ++){
               qiuruikai *= 2;
           }
           document.write(qiuruikai)
      </script>
</head>
<body>
    <h4>注意一下：infinity算错误，因为输入的数字太大了</h4>
    <br><br><button type="button" onclick="alert('qrk原创，禁止盗用,本人QQ：2669803073')">本站信息</button>
</body>
</html>
